# 📺 Media Recommendation API

A backend API built with **NestJS**, **Prisma ORM**, and **MySQL** to manage creators, users, media, and personalized media suggestions based on user activity.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🧑‍💻 Full CRUD operations for:
  - Users
  - Creators
  - Media
  - Media Types
  - Media Status (watch/like data)
- 🔍 **Extra methods beyond CRUD:**
  - Filter media by `title`, `genre`, `creator`, and `release year`
  - **Media suggestions** based on collaborative filtering logic
- ✅ Schema validation using `class-validator`
- 🔐 JWT-based authentication setup (strategy configured)
- 🛠 Prisma ORM for type-safe and efficient DB access

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

- **Framework:** [NestJS](https://nestjs.com/)
- **ORM:** [Prisma](https://www.prisma.io/)
- **Database:** MySQL
- **Validation:** class-validator
- **Authentication:** JWT with Passport.js

